{"tid":2427283,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[倉頡]點解喺windows pc會打唔到「揸」呢個字出嚟？","createTime":"2021-02-28T16:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T11:23:11.000Z","uid":5891,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"09dabf765379ef22aaf6fbbde14acd3fe99b1db2","tid":2427283,"uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T16:29:53.000Z","msg":"有次我喺電腦想打揸車個「揸」字出嚟，但係點打都打唔到出嚟<br />\n明明倉頡碼係「手木日一」冇錯呀<br />\n我喺手機就可以打到，但喺電腦就打唔到<br />\n後尾我用速成打「手一」，先check到佢個寫法係「剔手邊+査」，即係：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NJB2jJy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNJB2jJy.jpg&h=ca76ad0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以如果你用倉頡想打就要改成「手木月一」<br />\n<br />\n但係由細到大我學開個寫法都係「剔手邊+查」，即係：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4anjJ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4anjJ0.jpg&h=6fa6ac60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解windows（我用緊windows 10...以前都冇意識到呢個問題，應該係windows 10呢啲新版本先係咁）會冇得顯示「手+查」，仲要連倉頡碼都改埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實新輸入法都有幾多字倉頡碼係有變動，打打下會打唔到，好唔順手<br />\n有時會諗如果細個唔係學開倉頡，學粵語輸入法應該打得快好多"},{"pid":"3069589ddaadc83a293a1573e5221be8f934c212","tid":2427283,"uid":30836,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T17:28:22.000Z","msg":"Google:<br />\nwin10 香港增補字符集"},{"pid":"ede27de8f79b07790361aa563432c6e87793945b","tid":2427283,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3069589ddaadc83a293a1573e5221be8f934c212","tid":2427283,"uid":30836,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T17:28:22.000Z","msg":"Google:<br />\nwin10 香港增補字符集"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T17:29:23.000Z","msg":"冇睇內文 當我冇講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae626d580b20f0ad3df6bdae2b23a40abc75e8a9","tid":2427283,"uid":37097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T18:35:44.000Z","msg":"倉頡3代5代拆字唔同<br />\nWindows 幾十年黎都用3代，唔通冇啦啦轉去5代咩"},{"pid